			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Just to clear a few things up with people about what these are used for:<BR>
-Yes, they are used in some quests as mentioned before.<BR>
<BR>
Put these in a sewing kit to make things:<BR>
-2 spiderling silks=1 silk thred.<BR>
-2 silk threads=1 silk bandage.<BR>
-3 silk threads=1 silk cord.<BR>
-1 silk cord + ruined wolf pelt=tailored wrist pouch: weight:0.3, slots:4, size capacity: tiny. weight reduction: 10%, trivial: 26.<BR>
<BR>
There are other recipies that use pelts and silk cords, but im not giving them away.
				</font>
			</td>

