				Some more recipies with spiderling silk:<BR>
<BR>
silk thread (2 silks)+ lq skin = leather padding, used by smiths to make fs armor.<BR>
<BR>
silk chord (3 silks)+ grizzly skin = bearskin potion bag, useful 10 slot backpack for small item only.. sells for about 20-50p<BR>
<BR>
Sothz, Shadowknight of the 16th season
